query:
SELECT DISTINCT rl.gestorId, u.name as gestorNome, COUNT(*) as totalRelatorios
FROM relatorios_livres rl
INNER JOIN gestores g ON rl.gestorId = g.id
INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
GROUP BY rl.gestorId, u.name
ORDER BY totalRelatorios DESC;
